name: Schoolcode
body:
### Welcome to my SchoolCode Page.
This is a collection of source code that I've written over the course of my undergrad and master's studies.  As most of it was a learning experience it is hardly the pinnacle of my abilities, but I do like looking back to the before and after.
tagline: Old code from various school projects.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
